---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import { BRAND, CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../lib/siteConfig';
---

<LandingLayout title="Terms">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 md:py-40">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-16">Terms</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-600 space-y-16 leading-relaxed">
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-8 font-medium">We'll keep this simple and human.</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">What this tool is</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">{BRAND.PREFIX}<span class="text-red-600 font-bold">{BRAND.HIGHLIGHT}</span>{BRAND.SUFFIX} is an informational tool to help you understand your fertility based on the data you enter.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">What this tool is NOT</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-3 text-lg">
          <li>It is not medical advice</li>
          <li>It is not contraception</li>
          <li>It is not a medical device</li>
          <li>It is not guaranteed to be correct</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">Human bodies vary. Data can be incomplete or wrong. The app can make mistakes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">Your responsibility</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-lg">You are responsible for the decisions you make using this tool.</p>
        <p class="text-lg">If a decision really matters, don't rely on this alone.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">No guarantees</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">We do our best to make the app accurate and reliable, but we provide it "as is", without any guarantees.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">You are responsible for keeping your account secure.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">We may change or update the app over time.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="pt-12 border-t border-slate-100 mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">In short</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">Use this as a helpful aid, not as something to blindly trust with important decisions.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>